data.description: WONDERFUL - 4 bed, 2.5 bath Beautiful home boasts a spacious and open floor plan with large master bedroom on the main floor!! New flooring in Master bedroom! The roof was replaced in 2018 , AC new in 2020, bathrooms remodeled. This home has a large, open kitchen with tons of cabinet space, low HOA. Lots of natural light and complete hurricane protection! Spacious screened patio with heated pool with private back yard (No neighbors behind you)! Close to shopping and great restaurants. Come and see this hidden gem in quiet neighborhood in the heart of Margate!!!
